  <brief_title>First-Line Gemcitabine Chemotherapy With Our Without Sunitinib In Advanced or Metastatic Pancreatic Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Randomized Phase II Trial With Gemcitabine Plus Sunitinib Versus Gemcitabine Alone in First-line Therapy of Metastatic or Locally Advanced Pancreatic Cancer</official_title>
