  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Primary objective: to evaluate whether the addition of sunitinib prolongates the
      Progression-Free Survival (PFS) in patients with advanced pancreatic cancer receiving
      first-line gemcitabine chemotherapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
